  • public class TestMiniPlan
extends MiniPlanUnitTestBase
    This class contains examples to show how to use MiniPlanTestBuilder to test a specific plan fragment (MiniPlan). Each testcase requires 1) a RecordBatch, built from PopBuilder/ScanBuilder, 2)an expected schema and base line values, or 3) indicating no batch is expected.
